<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Voucher Template</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            page-break-after: always;
        }
        .page {
            width: 216mm;
            height: 303mm;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 10mm;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        .voucher {
            width: 196mm;
            height: 283mm;
            border: 2px solid #ccc;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .voucher-header {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .voucher-content {
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .voucher-footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #909090;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="voucher">
            <div class="voucher-header">Voucher Title</div>
            <div class="voucher-content">
                <p>Congratulations! You have received a special voucher.</p>
                <p>Use this voucher to enjoy exclusive benefits.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="voucher-footer">Valid until: <%= expirationDate %></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="voucher">
            <div class="voucher-content">
                <p>Terms and Conditions:</p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
